{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"022b22ee-07f0-45b3-b9ea-a08c260596ce","content":"Here's what you need to set up trusted publishing (OIDC) for NuGet:\n\n## 1. Configure NuGet.org Trusted Publisher\n\nOn [nuget.org](https://www.nuget.org), go to your package (or account settings for new packages):\n\n- **Manage Packages → Your Package → Trusted Publishers** (or for new packages: **Account → Trusted Publishers**)\n- Add a GitHub Actions publisher with:\n  - **Repository owner:** `myorg`\n  - **Repository:** `mylib`\n  - **Workflow:** `publish.yml`\n  - **Environment:** `nuget` (recommended)\n\n## 2. GitHub Actions Workflow","toolRequests":[{"toolCallId":"tooluse_XzDNsrBevcHJWf6Zo2rfb9","name":"create","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-c841b5e070ff4366bea83d6b86eaee52/.github/workflows/publish.yml","file_text":"name: Publish to NuGet\n\non:\n  push:\n    tags:\n      - 'v*'\n\njobs:\n  publish:\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    environment: nuget\n    permissions:\n      id-token: write # Required for OIDC trusted publishing\n\n    steps:\n      - uses: actions/checkout@v4\n\n      - uses: actions/setup-dotnet@v4\n        with:\n          dotnet-version: '8.0.x'\n\n      - name: Pack\n        run: dotnet pack src/MyLib/MyLib.csproj -c Release -o ./artifacts\n\n      - name: Publish to NuGet\n        run: dotnet nuget push ./artifacts/*.nupkg --source https://api.nuget.org/v3/index.json\n"},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"create a new file at /tmp/sv-c841b5e070ff4366bea83d6b86eaee52/.github/workflows/publish.yml."}],"interactionId":"65be9021-35d1-4b5a-9117-c1241cd31ad3","outputTokens":450,"requestId":"B811:246CF2:CA2BCE:E8DF2B:69F2A8B5"},"id":"8342cc8c-9767-456b-952f-3d4632ddd9f9","timestamp":"2026-04-30T00:56:30.557Z","parentId":"5696ecc1-199f-435d-9e9b-b05c341e8e38"}
{"type":"tool.execution_start","data":{"toolCallId":"tooluse_XzDNsrBevcHJWf6Zo2rfb9","toolName":"create","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-c841b5e070ff4366bea83d6b86eaee52/.github/workflows/publish.yml","file_text":"name: Publish to NuGet\n\non:\n  push:\n    tags:\n      - 'v*'\n\njobs:\n  publish:\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    environment: nuget\n    permissions:\n      id-token: write # Required for OIDC trusted publishing\n\n    steps:\n      - uses: actions/checkout@v4\n\n      - uses: actions/setup-dotnet@v4\n        with:\n          dotnet-version: '8.0.x'\n\n      - name: Pack\n        run: dotnet pack src/MyLib/MyLib.csproj -c Release -o ./artifacts\n\n      - name: Publish to NuGet\n        run: dotnet nuget push ./artifacts/*.nupkg --source https://api.nuget.org/v3/index.json\n"}},"id":"e147933c-2cd4-4499-8606-48a8955b8083","timestamp":"2026-04-30T00:56:30.557Z","parentId":"8342cc8c-9767-456b-952f-3d4632ddd9f9"}
